  "title": "Hits widget: transformData functions should be called even if the templates are not specified",
  "body": "The current behavior is to **not** call the `transformData` function if the associated (same name) `template` is not defined. I think it makes a lot of sense to distinguish those 2 concepts and call the `transformData` whatever the defined templates.\n",
